## Disaster Recovery Targets

| Parameter | Target | Implementation |
|---|---|---|
| RPO (Recovery Point) | < 1 hour | Continuous WAL replication + hourly snapshots |
| RTO (Recovery Time) | < 4 hours | Automated failover + documented runbooks |
| Backup frequency | Continuous WAL + daily full | Supabase WAL + daily pg_dump to S3 |
| Daily backup retention | 30 days | S3 lifecycle policy |
| Monthly backup retention | 12 months | S3 lifecycle policy |
| Geographic redundancy | Multi-region | Primary: ca-central-1, Replica: us-east-1 |
| Recovery testing | Quarterly | Chaos engineering + full restore drill |

